# Cross-OS safety: this repo is edited on Windows (CRLF) but every one of these
# files is EXECUTED on Linux (Replit, Docker containers). A CRLF shell script
# fails there with `bad interpreter: /usr/bin/env bash^M`, so pin them to LF
# in the repo and on checkout regardless of core.autocrlf.
*.sh        text eol=lf
.replit     text eol=lf
Dockerfile* text eol=lf
*.yml       text eol=lf
*.yaml      text eol=lf
